      "document_id": "document:manual-doc-001",
      "citation": "Project-authored starter document for FoliarShield-AI retrieval workflow validation; replace with license-compatible public literature before benchmarking.",
      "text": "FoliarShield-AI starts with rice as an agriculturally relevant cereal leaf and a waxy brassica or cabbage-type leaf as a difficult-to-wet hydrophobic benchmark. Fast assay labels include droplet impact, contact-line motion, spray coverage, retained fluorescent intensity, wash-off, evaporation, and early release. Living-payload assays remain contained and review-gated.",
