      "citation": "Project-authored starter document for FoliarShield-AI retrieval workflow validation; replace with license-compatible public literature before benchmarking.",
      "text": "FoliarShield-AI uses a batched, tiered discovery loop. Surrogate models estimate outcomes and uncertainty from fast physical assays, then Bayesian optimization proposes the next formulation batch under safety, feasibility, sprayability, material, and responsible-use constraints. The LLM agent retrieves evidence, explains hypotheses, checks constraints, and prepares auditable rationales for human review.",
